name: Surprise Counter Assault
Lore: 'Chief Chirpa led his Ewok warriors in a counterattack that captured many Imperial soldiers outside the Endor control bunker.',
Text: 'Cancel Counter Assault. OR Use 4 Force to cancel opponent''s Force drain at an exterior Endor site. Deploy (for free) from Reserve Deck any number of non-unique Ewoks to that site (Dark Side characters, vehicles and starships here may ''escape'' to Used Pile).',
